g.text: Recommended voltage divider for VBUS sensing on PA9.
As a 5V tolerant pin, it can be max. VDD+4V.
Situation where the MCU is not powered and 5V VBUS is connected to PA9 must be avoided.
1 Pair each close to their pins, 2u2 and 10n caps optional
